OL,3,CEx-miners extend strike at the
OL,4,Cnational pit museum
OL,6,FWorkers at the National Coal Mining
OL,7,FMuseum have extended their strike in a
OL,8,Fdispute over pay.
OL,10,FFormer miners who walked out during
OL,11,Fthe the 1984-5 strike are among those
OL,12,Fback on strike at the museum in
OL,13,FWakefield.
OL,15,FAbout 40 members of the union Unison
OL,16,Flaunched the action in August after
OL,17,Fclaims managers failed to improve a
OL,18,Fpay offer.
