OL,3,CEx-miners extend strike at the
OL,4,Cnational pit museum
OL,6,FThe strike, which was expected to last
OL,7,Funtil 14 September, has now been
OL,8,Fextended to mid-October.
OL,10,FUnderground tours have been suspended,
OL,11,Fbut the rest of the museum remains
OL,12,Fopen.
OL,14,FOn Monday 1 September, trade union
OL,15,FUNISON's Yorkshire and Humberside
OL,16,Fregional organiser Rianne Hooley said:
OL,17,F"For staff at the coal mining museum,
OL,18,Fthis isn't just a job. It's an
OL,19,Fopportunity to keep the area's coal
OL,20,Fmining heritage alive through their
OL,21,Fstorytelling.
