OL,6,F"We do not consider UNISON's pay claim
OL,7,Fto be reasonable or affordable in the
OL,8,Fcurrent economic environment."
OL,10,FMartin Fisher went along to speak to
OL,11,Fthe workers when the strike started in
OL,12,FAugust
OL,14,FRuss Kear reflected on returning to a
OL,15,Fpicket line after striking in the 80s.
OL,16,FHe said: "It's nowt like 1984-85, you
OL,17,Fwere against a government and this
OL,18,Ftime we're not against as many people.
