OL,6,F"You'd have said that was going to be
OL,7,Fthe last strike to end all strikes,
OL,8,Fbut obviously not."
OL,10,FAnother former miner, Eric Richardson
OL,11,Fsaid: "They are asking our members to
OL,12,Fgo down a drift make it safe we change
OL,13,Fpipes in the shaft 140 metres deep.
OL,15,F"Your next step could be your last one.
OL,17,F"Electricians have done work in this
OL,18,Fmuseum which would have cost them
OL,19,Fthousands of pounds if contracted out
OL,20,Fand we are asking a fair pay for the
OL,21,Fjobs we are doing."
