OL,6,FIn March Unison rejected a 5% pay
OL,7,Fincrease for all staff.
OL,9,FA follow-up offer to increase
OL,10,Funderground guides' pay by #1 an hour
OL,11,F- alongside a 5% rise for all other
OL,12,Fstaff - was also rejected after Unison
OL,13,Fsaid it could give men, who make up
OL,14,Fmost of the underground guides, a
OL,15,Fgreater payrise than women.
